query:
SELECT 
  sr.id,
  sr.supplierId,
  sr.serviceType,
  sr.serviceLevel,
  sr.countryCode,
  sr.cityId,
  sr.rateUsdCents,
  sr.isServiceable,
  CASE 
    WHEN sr.cityId IS NOT NULL THEN CONCAT('City: ', pc.cityName)
    ELSE 'Country-wide'
  END as rate_scope
FROM supplierRates sr
LEFT JOIN supplierPriorityCities pc ON pc.id = sr.cityId
WHERE sr.supplierId = 240001
  AND (sr.countryCode = 'AU' OR sr.countryCode IS NULL)
ORDER BY sr.serviceType, sr.serviceLevel, sr.countryCode
LIMIT 30;
